lead_paragraph: The Washington Spirit women's soccer team on Wednesday played the U.S. national anthem while players were still in their locker rooms, preventing visiting star Megan Rapinoe from continuing her protest for social equality.

headline.print_headline: Soccer Team Plays U.S. National Anthem Early to Prevent Player Protest
